headline: DocuSign Shares Rise 4.7% Post Q2 Earnings & Revenue Beat
summary: DOCU's Q2 earnings and revenues beat estimates by 9.5% and 2.8%, respectively, boosting shares by 4.7% and fueling an upbeat FY26 outlook.
